<p>Facebook recently announced they're¬†<a href="https://media.fb.com/2018/01/11/news-feed-fyi-bringing-people-closer-together/">drastically cutting down</a>¬†the reach of organic (unpaid) posts in the newsfeed in favor of more &quot;meaningful&quot; content.</p>
